 aerosmith60@... wrote:Hydras nodded. "Yes indeed you will get to slag something." Hydras comm'ed Quilldart. "I have an idea. Do you still have the sensor covers?" Quilldart looked over and saw them pilled in the corner where he had left them. "Yes sir, and im glad I make extra." Hydras slapped his hands together. "Alright heres the plan we each get a sensor disguiser. It will cover us from all thier sensors. We can leave ommiters in the base sending sensor ghosts of our numbers. As if preparing for the attack. They wont know weve left. At that point we'll be hiding in the forest and swamps to the south of the base. We can attack them from behind. It may give us a chance! We will still be outnumbers." He sent out a comm to the Rouges. "This is Hydras we are in need of your assistance immediatly, and we will be in debt to you. Please come to my base immediatly." Quilldart grabbed all the magnet bombs and he motiont for proto and starstorm to grab all the disguisers and headed to the base.
